    {
      "info": {
        "name": "Billing",
        "type": "folder"
      },
      "items": [
        {
          "info": {
            "name": "Gets a list of finalized past billing history",
            "type": "http"
          },
          "http": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "https://api.soracom.io/v1/bills",
            "auth": {
              "type": "apikey",
              "key": "X-Soracom-API-Key",
              "value": "{{X-Soracom-API-Key}}",
              "placement": "header"
            }
          },
          "docs": "Gets a list of finalized past billing history.\n\n**Warning**: The maximum information you can get is for the last 18 months. If you need the information before that time, please contact [Soracom Support](https://support.soracom.io).\n"
        },
        {
          "info": {
            "name": "Gets a finalized past billing history for the specified month",
            "type": "http"
          },
          "http": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "https://api.soracom.io/v1/bills/:yyyyMM",
            "params": [
              {
                "name": "yyyyMM",
                "value": "",
                "type": "path",
                "description": "Target year and month"
              }
            ],
            "auth": {
              "type": "apikey",
              "key": "X-Soracom-API-Key",
              "value": "{{X-Soracom-API-Key}}",
              "placement": "header"
            }
          },
          "docs": "Gets a finalized past billing history for the specified month. If you specify current month (the month in which the usage fee has not yet been finalized), you will get the preliminary value.\n\n**Warning**: The maximum information you can get is for the last 18 months. If you need the information before that time, please contact [Soracom Support](https://support.soracom.io).\n"
        },
        {
          "info": {
            "name": "Get a daily bill",
            "type": "http"
          },
          "http": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "https://api.soracom.io/v1/bills/:yyyyMM/daily",
            "params": [
              {
                "name": "yyyyMM",
                "value": "",
                "type": "path",
                "description": "Target year and month"
              }
            ],
            "auth": {
              "type": "apikey",
              "key": "X-Soracom-API-Key",
              "value": "{{X-Soracom-API-Key}}",
              "placement": "header"
            }
          },
          "docs": "Gets a daily bill for the specified month. Fees charged on a monthly basis cannot be retrieved. If you specify current month (a month for which the fee has not yet been finalized), a preliminary value will be returned.\n\n**Warning**: The maximum information you can get is for the last 18 months. If you need the information before that time, please contact [Soracom Support](https://support.soracom.io).\n"
        },
        {
          "info": {
            "name": "Export historical Detailed billing CSV to dedicated storage",
            "type": "http"
          },
          "http": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": "https://api.soracom.io/v1/bills/:yyyyMM/export",
            "params": [
              {
                "name": "yyyyMM",
                "value": "",
                "type": "path",
                "description": "Target year and month"
              },
              {
                "name": "export_mode",
                "value": "",
                "type": "query",
                "description": "Specify how to get the URL to download the billing details CSV.\n\n- `async`: Get the `exportedFieldId` without waiting for the URL to be issued on the Soracom platform. Specify this `exportedFieldId` in [Files:getExportedFile API](#!/Files/getExportedFile) to get the URL. If the file size of the billing details CSV is huge, use `async`.\n- `sync` (default): Wait for the URL to be issued on the Soracom platform. However, if the file size of the billing details CSV is huge, it may time out and the URL cannot be retrieved. If the timeout occurs, specify `async`.\n"
              }
            ],
            "auth": {
              "type": "apikey",
              "key": "X-Soracom-API-Key",
              "value": "{{X-Soracom-API-Key}}",
              "placement": "header"
            }
          },
          "docs": "Export historical [Detailed billing CSV](/en/docs/account/billing/#detailed-billing-csv) to dedicated storage and issue URL to download.\n\n**Warning**: The maximum information you can get is for the last 18 months. If you need the information before that time, please contact [Soracom Support](https://support.soracom.io).\n"
        },
        {
          "info": {
            "name": "Get latest bill",
            "type": "http"
          },
          "http": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "https://api.soracom.io/v1/bills/latest",
            "auth": {
              "type": "apikey",
              "key": "X-Soracom-API-Key",
              "value": "{{X-Soracom-API-Key}}",
              "placement": "header"
            }
          },
          "docs": "Retrieves the preliminary usage fee for the current month (the month in which the usage fee has not yet been finalized)."
        },
        {
          "info": {
            "name": "Export latest billing CSV file to S3",
            "type": "http"
          },
          "http": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": "https://api.soracom.io/v1/bills/latest/export",
            "params": [
              {
                "name": "export_mode",
                "value": "",
                "type": "query",
                "description": "Specify how to get the URL to download the billing details CSV.\n\n- `async`: Get the `exportedFieldId` without waiting for the URL to be issued on the Soracom platform. Specify this `exportedFieldId` in [Files:getExportedFile API](#!/Files/getExportedFile) to get the URL. If the file size of the billing details CSV is huge, use `async`.\n- `sync` (default): Wait for the URL to be issued on the Soracom platform. However, if the file size of the billing details CSV is huge, it may time out and the URL cannot be retrieved. If the timeout occurs, specify `async`.\n"
              }
            ],
            "auth": {
              "type": "apikey",
              "key": "X-Soracom-API-Key",
              "value": "{{X-Soracom-API-Key}}",
              "placement": "header"
            }
          },
          "docs": "Export [Detailed Billing CSV](/en/docs/account/billing/#detailed-billing-csv) for current month (the month in which the usage fee has not yet been finalized) to dedicated storage and issue a URL to download it. The fees will be finalized by the second business day of the following month. The Detailed billing CSV exported using this API will output preliminary values."
        },
        {
          "info": {
            "name": "Gets a billing summary of bill items.",
            "type": "http"
          },
          "http": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "https://api.soracom.io/v1/bills/summaries/bill_items",
            "auth": {
              "type": "apikey",
              "key": "X-Soracom-API-Key",
              "value": "{{X-Soracom-API-Key}}",
              "placement": "header"
            }
          },
          "docs": "Get a billing summary of bill items for the last 4 months (this month to 3 months ago).  Sorted by date from newest to oldest.\n\nThe summary you can get from this API is equivalent to the usage fees displayed in the [COSTS BY SERVICE] panel of the Billing Dashboard. For more information, please refer to [Billing Information](/en/docs/account/billing/).\n"
        },
        {
          "info": {
            "name": "Gets a billing summary of SIMs",
            "type": "http"
          },
          "http": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "https://api.soracom.io/v1/bills/summaries/sims",
            "auth": {
              "type": "apikey",
              "key": "X-Soracom-API-Key",
              "value": "{{X-Soracom-API-Key}}",
              "placement": "header"
            }
          },
          "docs": "Get a billing summary of SIMs for the last 4 months (current month to 3 months ago). Sorted by date from newest to oldest.\n\nThe summary you get from this API is equivalent to the rates displayed in the [COSTS PER SIM (TOP 100)] panel of the Rates Dashboard. For more information, please refer to [Billing Information](/en/docs/account/billing/).\n"
        }
      ]
    },
